# Project: Agent3D - Documentation-Driven Development Guidelines
# Type: Documentation Framework
# Created: 2024-01-18
# Purpose: Provides DDD guidelines and templates for LLM coding agents

# Documentation Structure:
# - README.md: Project overview and usage instructions
